org.shared.net.filter

Class IdentityFilterFactory<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.shared.net.filter.IdentityFilterFactory<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the inbound and outbound type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filter<T,T>, FilterFactory<OobFilter<T,T>,T,T,ConnectionHandler<?>>, OobFilter<T,T>

    public class IdentityFilterFactory<T>
extends Object
implements FilterFactory<OobFilter<T,T>,T,T,ConnectionHandler<?>>, OobFilter<T,T>
    An implementation of FilterFactory that creates identity filters, which simply pull values off of the input queue and push them onto the output queue.
